  "text": "Differential expression analysis: Differential gene expression was analyzed using DEseq2 (version 1.12.2) [CITATION_1] . The following parameters: DESeq(minReplicatesForReplace = Inf) and results(cooksCutoff = FALSE) were used in order to disable the Cook's filtering and flagging. Genes were defined as differentially expressed according to their padj<0.5.",
